name: FloatED-MOON (21) Gabu
description:
Hello, my name is Edmoon Holeworld
Humans usually called me The Moon.
Hiding behind our warm fur maybe comforts us.
But that is not hide who we are.
The higher being made us, and we made our self.
The environment shapes us, and I want to wrapped it all into my ideals.
But in the end, It can't be done alone.
